item.title: Could someone post Mod Taharoks tut for his compiler
item.dc:creator: @KiIIer KiIIer
item.description:
@KiIIer wrote:

You don’t need the perfect compiler to compile. I’m assuming you don’t have your environmental variables set because you can’t fix this so…use this:

@echo off title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_02\bin\javac.exe" *.Java pause
